{"tid":567683,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想知連登仔分得清心態同心理質素未","createTime":"2018-02-21T05:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T09:07:53.000Z","uid":113333,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1fee5d6005df16befd73e56cec3b0d43f52663","tid":567683,"uid":113333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:46:00.000Z","msg":"心態係指你個態度 例如你平時訓練認唔認真 落場有無俾心機踢或者有無跟教練指示做<br />\n心理質素係指當你面對緊張或者劣勢既時候可唔可以發揮到本身應有既水準<br />\n<br />\n根本科蘭由頭到尾都係講緊球員心理質素要改善 連登仔就結果論 一沉百踩 又話d球員無心踢又乜乜柒柒 俾著我係ky踢足全場見到呢d留言真係噴血 唔講仲以為傑志一開波就踢個波俾人之後11個人縮哂入小禁區守<br />\n<br />\n而事實就係傑志尋日其實係做到一D唔錯既攻勢出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/133753_c0201496f6d9bd6e17d846d416999796.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F133753_c0201496f6d9bd6e17d846d416999796.png&h=426d2f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n控球時間亦唔係一面倒<br />\n<br />\n我唔係唔俾人屌傑志 但你要屌都要屌d岩既野<br />\n尋晚場波單計球隊整體表現其實係ok 只係差好似科蘭所講既落後下既心理質素問題"},{"pid":"2369954e12bad0db697a468cf51ed2dd3d84a54f","tid":567683,"uid":113333,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:49:06.000Z","msg":"傑志第一樣要屌應該係聯賽重用假鬼<br />\n然後出到亞冠竟然要出李毅凱呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304fc023849abb79206bbb32af55fdd7c2e20bcf","tid":567683,"uid":2883,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:50:29.000Z","msg":"樓主咁勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb18786feecf528dc0d46b7a0729e40583663f9","tid":567683,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d1f06f00e5a12d93e317e54dba273cb572c68a4","tid":567683,"uid":113333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"304fc023849abb79206bbb32af55fdd7c2e20bcf","tid":567683,"uid":2883,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:50:29.00